{"word":"G1816 - ἐξανατέλλω - exanatéllō - ex-an-at-el'-lo - Spring up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξανατέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exanatéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-an-at-el'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Spring up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முளை"},{"paragraph":"1. to make spring up, to cause to shoot forth"},{"paragraph":"2. to spring up"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G393 - ἀνατέλλω - anatéllō - an-at-el'-lo/393\">G393</a>; to <i>start up out</i> of the ground, that is, <i>germinate:</i> - spring up.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}